{"tid":1050532,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實牙朗先唔好理球技,佢係皇馬最緊要係個壓場","createTime":"2019-03-07T03:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T02:19:42.000Z","uid":25345,"like":309,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"9997de6ebfb0b727d44cdcff428aabf95131f099","tid":1050532,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.bleacherreport.net/img/images/photos/003/590/611/hi-res-36e098c864c8be96e974d09a34c202b0_crop_exact.jpg?w=1200&amp;h=1200&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.bleacherreport.net%2Fimg%2Fimages%2Fphotos%2F003%2F590%2F611%2Fhi-res-36e098c864c8be96e974d09a34c202b0_crop_exact.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26h%3D1200%26q%3D75&h=8c3a5674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今季皇馬勁唔穩定,好似都試過6次輸3-0以上<br />\n牙朗係度有幾何會輸咁多? <br />\n而家逆境波廢到痴線,輸一球就繼續輸<br />\n成隊好似死狗咁,冇火冇神,眼神恐懼<br />\n牙朗根本係成隊既精神支柱,輸球後成隊覺得有佢係度就冇有怕<br />\n表現唔會走樣,佢既鬥志會感染到其他人<br />\n巴利同賓馬9成時間都係死狗樣<br />\n好啦就算佢地有火啦,其他人都未必服,成隊只有牙朗係令其他人心服,認同佢帶領<br />\n呢d真係天生領袖格,睇下個眼神個種火"},{"pid":"82e22261aa2f4e51a850f4a74709c71b2d32a45b","tid":1050532,"uid":30773,"like":35,"dislike":3,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:06:11.000Z","msg":"又潮文mode"},{"pid":"78c8d30cfed7883c4f2aa8e3bcc7f266b43fd0fd","tid":1050532,"uid":234938,"like":26,"dislike":90,"score":-64,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:09:05.000Z","msg":"壓場? 屌自己友就有佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e78f5cee2535d50e0aa75308b471194b5db3f8b","tid":1050532,"uid":25345,"like":157,"dislike":6,"score":151,"quote":{"pid":"78c8d30cfed7883c4f2aa8e3bcc7f266b43fd0fd","tid":1050532,"uid":234938,"like":26,"dislike":90,"score":-64,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:09:05.000Z","msg":"壓場? 屌自己友就有佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:10:40.000Z","msg":"班二打六唔屌咪攪成咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237f0c6be8e95cd5d38f424e37482874d